marketing-text: Whakatuwhera papaatapuna maatapuna ma te COVID19 raraunga. Papatohu paeutuhia me te taapiri tirotiro me te REST API taipitopito taipitopito, kua whakauruhia ki roto i nga reo katoa.

recovery-rate: Ko te reiti o te whakaoranga

promo-message: I hangaia ma te aroha ❤️ e te kapa i Hoobu.com. Whakamaahia to haerenga panui-mate i tenei wa me to maatau mahere whakamaataahi mo te waa-mahi whakamiharo
who-public-advice: Ko nga tohutohu a te iwi
general-advice-wash-hands-description: Me horoi noa o ringaringa me te 20 hēkona ma te whakamahi i te hopi me te wai i muri i to pupuhi i to ihu, te maru, te horoi ranei i mua i a koe e kai ana i te kai. Ko te horoi ringa tika ko te huarahi tino kaha mo te patu mate.
general-advice-minimise-contact-title: Te whakaiti i te whakapiri ake
general-advice-minimise-contact-descript: Whakaitihia nga hui koretake me nga haerenga me te rapu huarahi rereke ki nga mihi penei i te wiri o te ringa, te kihi, te kihi ranei.
general-advice-avoid-face-title: Kaua e pa ki to kanohi
general-advice-avoid-face-description: Ka taea e te ringaringa te hopu i nga huaketo me te paarua ano, ka taea e nga ringa te whakawhiti i te huaketo ki o kanohi, ihu, to waha ranei. Mai i reira, ka taea e te huaketo te uru ki o tinana me te mate.
general-advice-be-hygienic-description: Ko te hipoki i to waha me to ihu me to hiu piko ki to kiri ranei ka maremare koe i te maru, ki te turaki ranei i te kiko kua whakamahia.
general-advice-self-isolate-title: E mauiui ana te mate? Tuawhina!
general-advice-self-isolate-description: Mena ka tipu koe i te rewharewha penei i nga tohu ka mawehe koe i a koe ano me te tupato me te karo i te mate o te horapa atu o te mate ma te noho ki te kaainga.
strapline: Whakatuwhera papaatapuna maatauranga mo te raraunga COVID-19
